    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "えー！？　芽衣がもし恋のヒロインに選ばれたの！？\n怜ちゃんと渚ちゃんが出てたやつだよね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whaaat!? Mei was chosen as the heroine of Moshikoi!?\nIt’s that game Rei-chan and Nagisa-chan appeared‚ right!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。夏休み前の忙しいところ申し訳ないが\nぜひ芽衣に協力してほしいとのことだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Sorry to ask this of you when you’re busy before summer vacation‚\nbut they’d really like your cooperation‚ Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "楽しそう！　芽衣にやらせて！\nあのゲームのヒロインになれるなんて嬉しいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That sounds fun! Let Mei do it!\nI’m so happy to be the heroine of that game～！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣も怜ちゃんみたいに、最初は冷たいけど\n実は優しい子っていう設定だったりして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe Mei’s like Rei-chan‚ cold at first\nbut actually kind on the inside!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.8999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃんみたいな、幼なじみっていう設定もいいよね\n朝から家に「おはよー」って起こしに行くの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A childhood friend setting like Nagisa-chan would be nice too!\nI’ll go to his house in the morning and wake him up with a “Good morning”!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.2999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "ねえねえ、{user}さん！\n芽衣のお話はどんな感じになるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ hey‚ {user}-san!\nWhat will Mei’s story be like?",
        "id": ""
      },
